    public abstract class SwConcurrentResourceImpl
extends SwResourceImpl
implements SwConcurrentResource
    An implementation of the model object 'Sw Concurrent Resource'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Type
    • Activation Capacity
    • Entry Points
    • Adress Space
    • Period Elements
    • Priority Elements
    • Stack Size Elements
    • Activate Services
    • Enable Concurrency Services
    • Resume Services
    • Suspend Services
    • Terminate Services
    • Disable Concurrency Services
    • Share Data Resources
    • Message Resources
    • Mutual Exclusion Resources
    • Notification Resources
    • Heap Size Elements
